ActFarm Income Protection Act
SubjectAgri-Recovery - Manitoba Crop producers Assistance Program
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Agriculture and Agri-Food to provide assistance through the Agricultural Disaster Relief Program under the AgriRecovery Framework to Manitoba crop producers affected by excessive moisture through a contribution under the federal component of the 2010 Manitoba Interlake Unseeded Land Restoration Program.
